This repository contains public-safe reference architecture documentation,
examples, diagrams, and validation patterns for the TryNessa AI project.

TryNessa AI, TryNessa.com, NessaClaw, Secure Connector, Linked Devices, and
related product names are used to describe the TryNessa project and do not grant
trademark rights.

OpenClaw is referenced as an upstream open-source project where applicable:
https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw
NessaClaw is Nessa's guarded, managed product/integration surface built around
Nessa authentication, entitlement, policy, storage, audit, and safety controls.

Home Assistant is referenced as an upstream open-source smart-home project where
applicable:
https://www.home-assistant.io/
https://github.com/home-assistant
https://github.com/home-assistant/core

